name: molybdenum cofactor guanylyltransferase
reaction: GTP + molybdenum cofactor = diphosphate + guanylyl molybdenum cofactor [RN:R11581]
comment: Catalyses the guanylation of the molybdenum cofactor. This modification occurs only in prokaryotes.
